1 appropriations authorized from the general fund for a fiscal
2 year. In that event, to avoid an unconstitutional deficit,
3 the legislature may appropriate from the workforce development
4 and apprenticeship trust fund to the general fund only in the
5 amount necessary to meet general fund appropriations for that
6 fiscal year and only if the legislature has authorized
7 transfers from the appropriation contingency fund, the general
8 fund operating reserve and the tax stabilization reserve that
9 exhaust those fund balances." HB 7
